<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA514_06_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema514_06.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_06_ih_0001">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              <div class="fraction_box ml_0">
                <span>4</span>
                <span>9</span>
              </div>
              와
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>2</span>
                <span>3</span>
              </div>
              를 통분하여 크기를 비교해 보세요.
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center gap_40">
          <div class="bracket lg">
            <span class="bracket-l"></span>
            <div class="fraction_box">
              <span>4</span>
              <span>9</span>
            </div>
            <span class="comma">,</span>
            <div class="fraction_box">
              <span>2</span>
              <span>3</span>
            </div>
            <span class="bracket-r"></span>
          </div>
          <img src="../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg" class="obj_arrow" alt="" />
          <div class="bracket">
            <span class="bracket-l"></span>
            <div class="fraction_box">
              <span>4</span>
              <span>9</span>
            </div>
            <span class="comma">,</span>
            <div class="fraction_box">
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field></div>
              <span>9</span>
            </div>
            <span class="bracket-r"></span>
          </div>
          <img src="../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg" class="obj_arrow" alt="" />
          <div class="flex align_center gap_12">
            <div class="fraction_box">
              <span>4</span>
              <span>9</span>
            </div>
            <div class="dropdown_wrap">
              <select class="custom_dropdown math_symbol" data-answer-single="<">
                <option></option>
                <option value=">">></option>
                <option value="=">=</option>
                <option value="<"><</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="fraction_box">
              <span>2</span>
              <span>3</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">두 분모의 최소공배수인 9를 공통분모로 하여 통분한 후 분자의 크기를 비교합니다.</p>
                <div class="flex align_center gap_12">
                  <div class="bracket">
                    <span class="bracket-l"></span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span>9</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="comma">,</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>2</span>
                      <span>3</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="bracket-r"></span>
                  </div>
                  ➔
                  <div class="bracket">
                    <span class="bracket-l"></span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span>9</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="comma">,</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>2×3</span>
                      <span>3×3</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="bracket-r"></span>
                  </div>
                  ➔
                  <div class="bracket">
                    <span class="bracket-l"></span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span>9</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="comma">,</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>6</span>
                      <span>9</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="bracket-r"></span>
                  </div>
                  ➔
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>4</span>
                    <span>9</span>
                  </div>
                  &lt;
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <span>3</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
